{"tid":2115441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果㩒一個掣可以令CCTVBuddy嘔錢，你會㩒幾多次？","createTime":"2020-07-19T13:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T13:54:56.000Z","uid":279333,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d568fa6585746b7c11b244f0b1896fba6216ec84","tid":2115441,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">原來你每撳一個嬲掣，就會令大台賺少1,500蚊，知唔知條數點計？慢慢話你知</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年無線下半年廣告收入急速下跌，賺少咗約5.15億元，而sayno2tvb團隊響2019年7月11日成立，即係上年大約有174個任務，當每個任務有2000嬲啦(其實可能更少)，咁我地條數即係<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">515,000,000港幣 / (2,000嬲 x 174日) = 1,480.</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n即係每個嬲會令大台賺少1,500蚊！？唔係掛，原來消費者既意見真係咁重要嫁喎？正宗係「<strong><span class=\"red\">無成本又可以玩野，點解唔玩？」</span></strong> 和你Shop搞唔成啦，參加吓「電子版和你Shop」都好丫嘛，唔係要出街出汗先叫做咗野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5u5LTMMlOSgozJy3TB5K3XsOYIk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EF2Z5SJKYTA45CF5ZFDAV5E4OE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5u5LTMMlOSgozJy3TB5K3XsOYIk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEF2Z5SJKYTA45CF5ZFDAV5E4OE.jpg&h=12f0c665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">Source: 《TVB遭網民抵制 去年下半年廣告收入按年少5億》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200325/RQXEJ4EW5EBY6RWK26NVOMVESU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200325%2FRQXEJ4EW5EBY6RWK26NVOMVESU%2F&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=c61627e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200325%2FRQXEJ4EW5EBY6RWK26NVOMVESU%2F&h=4ab92810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200325/RQXEJ4EW5EBY6RWK26NVOMVESU/</a></span></em><br />\n<p class=\"center\">============================================</p><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">呢個禮拜做咗五個任務，響<strong><span class=\"red\">本周之星Pizza-BOX揚升帶動下，本周平均嬲數為670，較上星期高出70嬲，高於市場預期</span></strong>。</span><br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">無線新聞立場偏頗、時常斷章取義，多年來誤導不少港人，懇請 貴公司轉用其他宣傳渠道，例如ViuTV及77台，以免間接資助一間為中共維穩的電視台！而在 貴公司重新審視宣傳策略前，我及我的親朋戚友將會盡量避免光顧 貴公司，敬請注意。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，我地做個一周任務重溫！(截至19 Jul 2045)<br />\n<br />\n【18 Jul (六)】Crocodile <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x 470<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/crocodilehk/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcrocodilehk%2Fposts&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=52724580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/crocodilehk/posts</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【17 Jul (五)】立邦油漆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x 629<br />\n<span class=\"small\">香港地區: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nipponpainthongkong/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnipponpainthongkong%2Fposts&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=7c48aebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nipponpainthongkong/posts</a><br />\n日本地區: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nptu.nipponpaint/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnptu.nipponpaint%2Fposts&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=235b2ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nptu.nipponpaint/posts</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【16 Jul (四)】新三國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x 531<br />\n呢間野會Block人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/3KD.MFG/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F3KD.MFG%2Fposts&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=8e5b95af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/3KD.MFG/posts</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【15 Jul (三)】澳洲歌婷床上用品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x 625<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/Cottex/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FCottex%2Fposts%2F&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=5093edec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/Cottex/posts/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【14 Jul (二)】Pizza-BOX <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />x 1092<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/pizzaboxhk/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fpizzaboxhk%2Fposts&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=fb0a098b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/pizzaboxhk/posts</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【13 Jul (一)】澄清聲明 - 順達財務並非TVB廣告商！！！ </strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">============================================</p><br />\n今個禮拜因為廣告商打手頻繁出沒，為品牌洗Like護航，搞到樓主非常攰，要瘋狂捉佢地出黎舉報，涉事品牌包括Pizza-BOX、澳洲歌婷床上用品同埋新三國。另外，昨宵樓主再響花王潔霸發現逾二千名打手，懷疑係透過Jag香港平台招募，凝造品牌受廣泛歡迎既形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以下係一周花生回顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOQqc9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOQqc9k.jpg&h=3c184bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薄餅盒打手好敬業樂業，<strong><span class=\"red\">做打手做到好似開聊天室咁，洗咗成百個留言，務求將自己留言推上熱門置頂，覆蓋手足既抵制留言</span></strong>，奈何魔高一尺，樓主高一丈，ＳＤＴＬ啲小動作我都睇到，你地咁大動作想呃到邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">詳見：《再有打手集團被連根拔起！公關公司：仆街又廢咗十幾個Account》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2112378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2112378</a></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWtrSPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWtrSPy.jpg&h=a65a22fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翌日，<strong><span class=\"red\">澳洲歌婷亦用住同樣既「聊天室模式」＋「刪除留言」淨化自己既專頁</span></strong>，因入面個西洋女子竟然講到流利粵語，非常犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">詳見：《一開始WFH，啲網民無所事事又開始周圍咬人》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2109477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2109477</a></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-tpe1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/107737929_603333467225910_5431954857585416256_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=1480c5&amp;_nc_ohc=E0ajWURI-hMAX9SnyEB&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-tpe1-1.xx&amp;oh=47aa8d77730c952fa2b3e5ca013c5de5&amp;oe=5F3A6E59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-tpe1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F107737929_603333467225910_5431954857585416256_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D1480c5%26_nc_ohc%3DE0ajWURI-hMAX9SnyEB%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-tpe1-1.xx%26oh%3D47aa8d77730c952fa2b3e5ca013c5de5%26oe%3D5F3A6E59&h=919be7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">新三國亦出現類似打手</span></strong>，因為樓主無截圖，所以借用咗ＦＢ手足既圖片（樓主當時一直密切注視新三國啲留言，發現僅有既兩位打手之後消失咗，有機會被bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">============================================</p><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceK3x7w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceK3x7w.jpg&h=4ffcb97a&s={SIZE}\" /> 另外，有<strong><span class=\"red\">兩個之前關Page既紅媒金主已經再度上線</span></strong>啦，我相信佢地好多都<strong><span class=\"red\">抱持一種心態，就係「香港人都係善忘」，以為過一排開返Page就無事</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNonono，點解你地會有呢種錯覺嫁？講好咗要永久抵制2020年既TVB金主嫁嘛，點會唔記得你地呀？歡迎大家繼續請願，勸佢同紅媒割蓆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【沐印消毒水】<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/沐印-Hong-Kong-107297100940459/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%E6%B2%90%E5%8D%B0-Hong-Kong-107297100940459%2Fposts&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=669b9f04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/沐印-Hong-Kong-107297100940459/posts</a></span><br />\n【出入易迷你倉】<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/出入易迷你倉-In-N-Out-Storage-1111275085557250/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E6%98%93%E8%BF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%89-In-N-Out-Storage-1111275085557250%2Fposts%2F&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=99303153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/出入易迷你倉-In-N-Out-Storage-1111275085557250/posts/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">詳見：《起身鞭屍呀！！鞭完再鞭呀！！！》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2107795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2107795</a></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">============================================</p><br />\n如果想準時收到TVB任務，一定要響Facebook同Telegram follow sayno4tvb團隊（我唔係佢地團隊），又或者<strong><span class=\"red\">得閒click入呢個Post（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059659</a>）我會盡量每日更新</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8podddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=8255a673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayn